                <p><strong>Myth 2: "Ek hafte mein baal 1 inch badh sakte hain."</strong> — Biologically impossible hai. Maximum growth 0.5 inch per month hoti hai. Agar aap is topic pe zyada jaanna chahte hain toh hamari <a href="how-to-grow-hair-in-1-week-reality-check.php">reality check guide on growing hair in 1 week</a> padhein.</p>

